criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy subjects

          -  Written and informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or breastfeeding women;

          -  Subject enrolled in another study excluding co-enrolment;

          -  Cardio-vascular or respiratory disease;

          -  History of ear nose and throat disease (i.e. surgery, epistaxis, trauma), eso-gastric
             disease (i.e. esophageal varices, digestive haemorrhage), rheumatologic or neurologic
             disease possibly interfering with the design of the study;

          -  Subject feeling nauseous or under recent fed condition (<1h).
